<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two adjoining fragments of a rectangular <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.90</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.31</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.45</measure>) moulded on the front face (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.85</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.31</measure>). All edges and some parts of the face are chipped.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.83</measure> wide), with some overlap onto the mouldings in lines 1 and 6.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Late second to early third century; l.1, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.022</measure>, l.2, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.02</measure>, l.3, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.018</measure>, l.4, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.02</measure>, l.5, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.024</measure>, l.6, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.022</measure>: dot for stop; ligatures: <foreign lang="grc">ΜΗ</foreign>, l.1.  Diairetic dots around <foreign lang="grc">Α</foreign> of <foreign lang="grc">Ἀθηναγόραν</foreign> (l. 2), final <foreign lang="grc">Υ</foreign> (l. 2), <foreign lang="grc">Ε</foreign> of <foreign lang="grc">ἀρχιερείας</foreign> (l. 3), <foreign lang="grc">Α</foreign> of <foreign lang="grc">ΑΝΑ</foreign> (l. 4), Ε of ἐποήσατο, l.5, Α of βία, second Α of Ἀπφία, Υ of ὑπέσχετο, l.6.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notAfter="0300" notBefore="0201" exact="none">Third century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>, <rs type="criteria">prosopography</rs>)</p>
</div>
